is made by CD Projekt Red, the studio that brought us The Wisher series and is one of the most eagerly

13:17.680 --> 13:23.760
awaited games of the last few years. You dive into a dark, dystopian future where incredible technology

13:23.760 --> 13:29.200
is redefining who and what we are. You can become part of this stunningly large world with immersive

13:29.200 --> 13:34.560
storytelling. Here's the thing, we haven't played the game yet, but when you see this video, we're

13:34.560 --> 13:40.240
probably already doing so. If the past work of CD Projekt Red is any indication, then this will be

13:40.240 --> 13:45.200
an amazing game, which is why we did this collaboration and sat on this video for far

